  "title": "Clinic Receptionist| O&G Clinic",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><ul><li>Assist to book and arrange appointment for patient</li><li>Assist in dispensing of medicines with doctor's prescription</li><li>Assist in managing smooth clinic operations and maintaining clinical & service quality</li><li>Registration of patients and providing customer service</li><li>Process of billing/insurance agency transactions with different stakeholders</li><li>Manage inventory and replenish of medicines and consumable items</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>At least 2 years of working experience in O&G Clinic</li><li>Min O level</li></ul><p>Check Aber Care Website for more details.</p><p><br /></p><p>Interested applicants may email your updated resume to career@abercare.sg.</p><p><br /></p><p>Abercare.sg | EA License No. 18C9070 | KOH SU WEN, CLARISSA| Registration No. R24119504</p>",
